          '正确顺序是“先读后写，先低风险后高风险”。这条顺序可以让你在保持收益的同时，尽可能降低事故概率。',
          '每多一个接入点，都要问自己：如果它失败，我能否快速定位？如果它被滥用，我能否及时收口？'
        ]
      }
    ],
    cards: [
      {
        term: '跨工具编排',
        explanation: '将多个工具按步骤组合为单条业务流程。',
        whyItMatters: '把分散操作压缩成一次性产出，显著降低上下文切换。'
      },
      {
        term: '权限最小化',
        explanation: '只给当前任务必需权限，并设置过期策略。',
        whyItMatters: '降低凭证泄露和误操作带来的影响半径。'
      },
      {
        term: '来源可追溯',
        explanation: '输出中保留引用与证据链。',
        whyItMatters: '结果可验证，决策更可靠。'
      }
    ]
  },
  5: {
    intro: '今天你会发现，技能系统不是“插件商店”，而是组织能力的供应链。',
    chapters: [
      {
        title: '第一章：技能的本质是“可复用行为单元”',
        paragraphs: [
          '一个优秀技能不是“功能多”，而是“边界清晰、输入输出稳定”。它像工厂里的标准零件，可以被重复装配到不同场景。',
          '当你用这种视角看技能，你就不会再盲目追数量。'
        ]
      },
      {
        title: '第二章：安装后验证比安装动作本身更重要',
        paragraphs: [
          '安装只是开始。你必须给每个技能配一条验证样例，确保在当前环境下可实际调用且结果可控。',
          '没有验证样例的技能，等同于“潜在故障源”。'
        ]
      },
      {
        title: '第三章：从插件堆积走向链路设计',
        paragraphs: [
          '真正有用的做法是把技能串成链：信息输入、加工处理、结果分发。每个节点可替换、可重试、可审计。',
          '这也是你从“个人玩家”走向“系统设计者”的关键一步。'
        ]
      }
    ],
    cards: [
      {
        term: '技能契约',
        explanation: '定义技能输入字段、输出格式与异常行为。',
        whyItMatters: '契约稳定，链路才稳定。'
      },
      {
        term: '版本锁定',
        explanation: '固定技能版本并记录升级策略。',
        whyItMatters: '防止“昨天能跑今天失效”的漂移问题。'
      },
      {
        term: '链路审计',
        explanation: '记录每次调用的参数、结果和状态。',
        whyItMatters: '有据可查，才能持续优化和快速止损。'
      }
    ]
  },
  6: {
    intro: '从今天开始，你的助手会在你不在场时继续工作，这就是生产力复利的开始。',
    chapters: [
      {
        title: '第一章：主动化的核心是“可控自动”',
        paragraphs: [
          '自动化并不等于无人值守。真正好的主动化是“平时自动、异常可控、必要时可一键停”。',
          '你需要把任务生命周期设计完整：触发、执行、重试、告警、终止。'
        ]
      },
      {
        title: '第二章：没有监控，就没有优化',
        paragraphs: [
          '很多团队上线自动化后依旧焦虑，因为看不到过程。可观测性不是附加功能，而是自动化系统的一部分。',
          '当你能看见失败类型和耗时分布，优化路径就会非常清晰。'
        ]
      },
      {
        title: '第三章：稳定性来自演练，而不是祈祷',
        paragraphs: [
          '故障不是“会不会发生”，而是“什么时候发生”。你今天必须故意制造一次失败，验证告警和恢复链路。',
          '演练做得越早，真实事故时你越冷静。'
        ]
      }
    ],
    cards: [
      {
        term: '失败优先设计',
        explanation: '先定义失败场景，再补成功路径。',
        whyItMatters: '现实世界里失败比成功更需要设计。'
      },
      {
        term: '告警可行动',
        explanation: '告警中必须包含定位信息与下一步建议。',
        whyItMatters: '减少“看到告警却不知道怎么办”的停滞。'
      },
      {
        term: '降级策略',
        explanation: '核心依赖不可用时切换到简化流程。',
        whyItMatters: '保障关键任务不中断。'
      }
    ]
  },
  7: {
    intro: '今天不是结束，而是把“能用”沉淀为“可长期运营”。',
    chapters: [
      {
        title: '第一章：从个人实验到系统治理',
        paragraphs: [
          '你已经证明了助手能带来价值，接下来要证明这套系统可以长期稳定、可审计、可交接。',
          '治理不是官僚流程，而是保护效率成果不被意外吞掉。'
        ]
      },
      {
        title: '第二章：安全、版本、成本是三条生命线',
        paragraphs: [
          '安全决定你敢不敢用，版本决定你稳不稳定，成本决定你能不能长期用。三者缺一不可。',
          '成熟团队会把这三条生命线写成固定节奏：周巡检、月复盘、季度升级策略。'
        ]
      },
      {
        title: '第三章：真正的优势来自时间累积',
        paragraphs: [
          '同样的模型，同样的工具，为什么有人效果越来越好？因为他持续积累上下文、规则和流程资产。',
          '从今天起，你的 AI 助手不是一次性项目，而是长期生产系统。越早进入运营节奏，优势越明显。'
        ]
      }
    ],
    cards: [
      {
        term: '运行基线',
        explanation: '一组不可妥协的最低运行标准。',
        whyItMatters: '防止系统在迭代中逐步失控。'
      },
      {
        term: '变更治理',
        explanation: '升级、回滚、验证必须形成标准流程。',
        whyItMatters: '避免“临场修复”引发连锁故障。'
      },
      {
        term: '复盘机制',
        explanation: '定期复盘失败、成本和收益。',
        whyItMatters: '把经验变成持续增长，而不是一次性记忆。'
      }
    ]
  }
};

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return Array.from({ length: 7 }, (_, i) => ({ params: { day: String(i + 1) } }));
}

const day = Number(Astro.params.day);
const plan = dayPlans.find((p) => p.day === day) ?? dayPlans[0];
const narrative = narratives[plan.day];
const story = storybook[plan.day];
const pageTitle = `第${plan.day}天：${plan.title} | 7天学习路径`;
const pageDescription = `OpenClaw 7天学习路径第${plan.day}天：${plan.subtitle}。目标：${plan.goal}，${plan.duration}。`;
const canonicalUrl = `https://aiopenclaw.app/day/${plan.day}/`;

const breadcrumbItems = [
  { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: '首页', item: 'https://aiopenclaw.app/' },
  { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: '7天学习路径', item: 'https://aiopenclaw.app/#learning-path' },
  { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 3, name: `第${plan.day}天`, item: canonicalUrl }
];

const jsonLd = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@graph': [
    {
      '@type': 'WebPage',
      name: pageTitle,
      description: pageDescription,
      url: canonicalUrl,
      inLanguage: 'zh-CN',
      isPartOf: { '@type': 'WebSite', name: 'awesome openclaw', url: 'https://aiopenclaw.app/' }
    },
    { '@type': 'BreadcrumbList', itemListElement: breadcrumbItems },
    {
      '@type': 'HowTo',
      name: `OpenClaw 第${plan.day}天学习计划`,
      description: plan.goal,
      step: plan.steps.map((step, index) => ({
        '@type': 'HowToStep',
        position: index + 1,
        name: step.title,
        text: step.detail
      }))
    }
  ]
};
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/ai-openclaw-logo.png" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/images/ai-openclaw-logo.png" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonicalUrl} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:title" content={pageTitle} />
    <meta property="og:url" content={canonicalUrl} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={pageDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://aiopenclaw.app/images/ai-openclaw-logo.png" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={pageTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={pageDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://aiopenclaw.app/images/ai-openclaw-logo.png" />
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify(jsonLd)} />
    <style>
      .day-hero {
        background:
          radial-gradient(760px 520px at 78% 18%, rgba(93, 125, 255, 0.42), transparent 70%),
          radial-gradient(620px 520px at 88% 75%, rgba(29, 190, 177, 0.2), transparent 70%),
          linear-gradient(125deg, #071634 0%, #0a234f 45%, #0d2f66 76%, #0a2554 100%);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(66, 107, 176, 0.45);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 overflow-x-hidden">
    <section class="day-hero">
      <SiteHeader active="learning" />
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:py-16 text-white">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-sm mb-4">📅 7天学习路径 · Day {plan.day}</div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight">第{plan.day}天：{plan.title}</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-blue-100 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-3xl">{plan.subtitle}</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 sm:py-12 space-y-8">
      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-blue-500/60 bg-blue-50 text-slate-800 rounded-r-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm sm:text-base italic">
          {narrative.quote}
        </blockquote>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">章节导读</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">{story.intro}</p>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          {plan.intro.map((paragraph) => (
            <p>{paragraph}</p>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500">⏱ {plan.duration}</p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">故事主线</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-6">
          {story.chapters.map((chapter) => (
            <article>
              <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">{chapter.title}</h3>
              <div class="mt-2 space-y-3 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                {chapter.paragraphs.map((p) => (
                  <p>{p}</p>
                ))}
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">{narrative.storyTitle}</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          {narrative.story.map((paragraph) => (
            <p>{paragraph}</p>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">对话片段</h3>
          <div class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            {narrative.dialogue.map((line) => (
              <p>{line}</p>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">今天你将完成</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
          {plan.chapterOverview.map((item) => (
            <li>{item}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">核心概念详解</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
          {plan.concepts.map((c) => (
            <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">{c.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">{c.text}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">知识卡片</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          {story.cards.map((card) => (
            <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">{card.term}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">{card.explanation}</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">为什么重要：{card.whyItMatters}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">一个典型工作流示例</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <th class="py-2 pr-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">时间</th>
                <th class="py-2 pr-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">动作</th>
                <th class="py-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">结果</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {plan.timeline.map((t) => (
                <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
                  <td class="py-2 pr-3 text-slate-600">{t.time}</td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-3 text-slate-700">{t.event}</td>
                  <td class="py-2 text-slate-700">{t.value}</td>
                </tr>
              ))}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">实操步骤</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
          {plan.steps.map((step, idx) => (
            <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">步骤 {idx + 1}：{step.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">{step.detail}</p>
              {step.command && (
                <pre class="mt-3 text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-slate-900 text-emerald-300 p-3"><code>{step.command}</code></pre>
              )}
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">完成判定：</span>{step.verify}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">可复制 Prompt 模板</h2>
        <pre class="mt-4 text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-slate-900 text-emerald-300 p-3"><code>{plan.promptTemplate}</code></pre>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">今日交付物</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
          {plan.deliverables.map((item) => (
            <li>{item}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">常见误区</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
          {plan.pitfalls.map((item) => (
            <li>{item}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">验收清单</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
          {plan.checklist.map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5 text-green-600">✓</span><span>{item}</span></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
          {plan.faq.map((qa) => (
            <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Q：{qa.q}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">A：{qa.a}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">参考资料</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          {plan.references.map((ref) => (
            <a href={ref.url} class="block rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-white hover:border-blue-300 transition px-4 py-3" {...(ref.url.startsWith('http') ? { target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener noreferrer' } : {})}>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">{ref.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 mt-1">查看资源 →</p>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to-blue-900 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">明日预告</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">{plan.preview}</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-blue-200">🐾 旁白：{narrative.reflection}</p>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 justify-between">
        {plan.day > 1 ? (
          <a href={`/day/${plan.day - 1}/`} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 font-semibold">← 上一天</a>
        ) : (
          <a href="/#learning-path" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 font-semibold">← 返回学习路径</a>
        )}
        {plan.day < 7 ? (
          <a href={`/day/${plan.day + 1}/`} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-semibold">下一天 →</a>
        ) : (
          <a href="/zh/resources/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-semibold">进入资源聚合页 →</a>
        )}
      </section>
    </main>

    <SiteFooter />
  </body>
</html>
